  <data name="GitLab is a trademark of GitLab Inc. Aiursoft provides deployment, hosting, and integration services for GitLab — we are not affiliated with or endorsed by GitLab Inc. The GitLab Community Edition (CE) is MIT-licensed and can be deployed freely. The GitLab Enterprise Edition (EE) requires a separate license purchased from GitLab Inc. We can assist you with procuring the appropriate GitLab EE license, or you may choose to remove this item from your plan." xml:space="preserve">
